## <a name="authentication-events"></a><span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-159">Udalosti služby overovania</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-159">Authentication events</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-160">Tieto udalosti diagnostických údajov sa zhromažďujú, keď sa Office pokúša získať token overenia, či už bez zobrazenia výzvy alebo prostredníctvom zobrazenia výzvy.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-160">These diagnostic data events are collected when Office attempts to acquire an authentication token, either silently or through prompting.</span></span>

### <a name="officeandroidmsaguesttoaad"></a><span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-161">Office.Android.MSAGuestToAAD</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-161">Office.Android.MSAGuestToAAD</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-162">Táto udalosť pomáha pri pochopení, koľkým používateľom sa zobrazuje výzva na zadanie hesla osobného konta pri prístupe k pracovnému zdroju, keďže ich osobné konto môže byť platným hosťom pre nájomníka pracovného konta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-162">This event helps in understanding how many users are getting prompted for providing personal account password, while accessing work resource, as their personal account could be a valid guest to work account's tenant.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-163">Tieto údaje nám pomáhajú porozumieť, koľkým používateľom sa zobrazujú opakované výzvy na prihlásenie na prioritizáciu získavania tokenov AAD bez výziev na základe kontrolného výrazu SAML (Security Assertion Markup Language) pre konto Microsoft.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-163">This data helps us understand how many users are going through the pain of sign in re-prompts to prioritize AAD token acquisition silently based on a Microsoft account SAML (Security Assertion Markup Language) assertion.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-164">Zhromažďujú sa tieto polia:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-164">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-165">**Tag** – označuje, že používateľovi sa zobrazila výzva na prihlásenie pre osobné konto počas pristupovania k pracovnému zdroju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-165">**Tag** - Indicates that user got sign-in prompt for personal account, while accessing work account resource.</span></span>


### <a name="officeidentityfbapromptwin32"></a><span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-166">Office.Identity.FbaPromptWin32</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-166">Office.Identity.FbaPromptWin32</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-167">Zhromažďuje sa, keď sa v balíku Office používateľovi zobrazí výzva na prihlásenie typu Forms-Based-Auth.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-167">Collected when Office shows the user a Forms-Based-Auth sign-in prompt.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-168">Spolu so získaním skrytého tokenu výzvy na overenie umožňujú určiť, či sa používateľ nachádza v stave nefunkčného overenia, čo pre používateľa znamená, že je buď stave offline klienta, alebo v horšom prípade môže nefunkčné overenie znemožniť získanie licencie a mať tak za následok, že klient bude úplne nepoužiteľný.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-168">Along with silent token acquisitions, authentication prompts is used to determine if user is in a broken authentication state which, for the user, results in what is essentially an Offline Client state, or in the worst case, broken authentication may prevent license acquisition and result in a completely unusable client.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-169">Výzvy na prihlásenie typu Forms-Based-Auth (FBA) sa používajú pre niektoré lokálne scenáre overovania a zvyčajne sa chceme uistiť, že sa to nedeje, pretože všetky by mali používať prihlásenie typu Modern-Auth z dôvodov chýb zabezpečenia súvisiacich s prihlásením typu FBA.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-169">Forms-Based-Auth (FBA) sign-in prompts are used for some on-premises authentication scenarios and typically we want to make sure this isn't happening, as everyone should be using Modern-Auth because of security vulnerabilities associated with FBA.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-170">Zhromažďujú sa tieto polia:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-170">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-171">**AuthScheme** – používaná schéma overovania</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-171">**AuthScheme** - the authentication scheme used</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-172">**DocumentUrlHash** – vyžadovanie šifrovanej URL adresy</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-172">**DocumentUrlHash** - an encrypted URL requesting</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-173">**EndTag** – značka, v ktorej je formulár FBA skončený</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-173">**EndTag** - the tag where FBA form is completed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-174">**Flags** – zastarané</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-174">**Flags** - Obsolete</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-175">**FlowTag** – značka, v ktorej je formulár FBA začatý</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-175">**FlowTag** - the tag where FBA form is started</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-176">**LastError** – vrátený kód chyby</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-176">**LastError** – the error code returned</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-177">**PromptEndTime** – čas skončenia výzvy</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-177">**PromptEndTime** - the time when then prompt ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-178">**PromptStartTime** – čas začatia výzvy</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-178">**PromptStartTime** - the time when the prompt started</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-179">**Result** – či bolo overenie úspešné</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-179">**Result** - whether the authentication succeeded</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-180">**SessionEndTime** – čas skončenia relácie udalosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-180">**SessionEndTime** – the time when the event session ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-181">**Timeout** – čas uplynutia časového limitu výzvy</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-181">**Timeout** - the time when the prompt timed out</span></span>

### <a name="officeidentitysignoutevent"></a><span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-182">Office.Identity.SignOutEvent</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-182">Office.Identity.SignOutEvent</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-183">Zhromažďuje sa, keď sa používateľ odhlási z balíka Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-183">Collected when a user signs out of Office.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-184">Vďaka informácii, že používateľ je odhlásený, je možné klasifikovať ďalšie udalosti, ako sú napríklad výzvy, ako očakávané, aby bolo tieto udalosti možné správne vypočítať v metrike spoľahlivosti/pripravenosti na odoslanie a predchádzať upozorneniam alebo návratu zostáv na predchádzajúcu verziu z dôvodu nesprávneho predpokladu, že používateľovi sa zobrazujú neočakávané výzvy na prihlásenie.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-184">Knowing the user is signed-out makes it possible to classify other events, such as prompts, as expected, so those events can be correctly computed in reliability / ship-readiness metrics and avoid alerting or rolling back builds on the faulty premise that the user is experiencing unexpected sign-in prompts.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-185">Zhromažďujú sa tieto polia:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-185">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-186">**FlowEndTime** – čas skončenia akcie odhlásenia</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-186">**FlowEndTime** - the time when the sign out action ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-187">**FlowStartTime** – čas začatia akcie odhlásenia</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-187">**FlowStartTime** - the time when the sign out action started</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-188">**IdentityErrorState** – akýkoľvek stav chyby identity počas odhlásenia</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-188">**IdentityErrorState** - any identity error state during sign out</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-189">**IdentityHashedUniqueId** – šifrovaný identifikátor identity, ktorá sa odhlasuje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-189">**IdentityHashedUniqueId** - the encrypted identity ID being signed out</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-190">**IdentityProviderType** – poskytovateľ identity odhlasovanej identity</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-190">**IdentityProviderType** - the identity provider of the identity being signed out</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-191">**IdentityUniqueId** – identifikátor identity, ktorá sa odhlasuje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-191">**IdentityUniqueID** - the identity ID being signed out</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-192">**SessionEndTime** – čas skončenia relácie udalosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-192">**SessionEndTime** - the time when the event session ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-193">**SignOutUserAction** – označuje, že používateľ inicioval akciu odhlásenia</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-193">**SignOutUserAction** - Indicates the user initiates the sign out action</span></span>

### <a name="officeidentitysspipromptwin32"></a><span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-194">Office.Identity.SspiPromptWin32</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-194">Office.Identity.SspiPromptWin32</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-195">Zhromažďuje sa, keď sa v balíku Office používateľovi zobrazí výzva na prihlásenie typu Windows SSPI.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-195">Collected when Office shows the user a Windows SSPI sign-in prompt.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-196">Spolu so získaním skrytého tokenu výzvy na overenie umožňujú určiť, či sa používateľ nachádza v stave nefunkčného overenia, čo pre používateľa znamená, že je stave offline klienta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-196">Along with silent token acquisitions, authentication prompts determine whether a user is in a broken authentication state, which results in an Offline Client state.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-197">Nefunkčné overenie môže znemožniť získanie licencie a mať tak za následok, že klient bude úplne nepoužiteľný.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-197">Broken authentication may prevent license acquisition and result in a completely unusable client.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-198">Výzvy typu Windows SSPI slúžia na overovanie so službou Exchange (na synchronizáciu pošty), keď prostriedok služby Exchange používateľa nebol nastavený na viacfaktorové overovanie.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-198">Windows SSPI prompts are used for authenticating with Exchange (for mail synchronizing) when the user's Exchange resource hasn't been setup for multi-factor authentication.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-199">Tieto udalosti, ako aj udalosti priestoru názvov Office.MATS, sa používajú na tieto účely:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-199">These events, along with the Office.MATS namespace events, are used for the following purposes:</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-200">1\) Identifikácia, či klienti dokážu úspešne získať overovací token alebo či prešli do stavu nefunkčného overenia.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-200">1\) Identify whether clients can successfully obtain an authentication token or have entered a broken authentication state.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-201">2\) Vyhodnotenie, či zmeny, ku ktorým došlo v klientovi alebo v službách, mali za následok kritické regresie pri postupe alebo spoľahlivosti overovania používateľa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-201">2\) Evaluate whether changes that have occurred on the client or services have resulted in critical regressions in the user's authentication experience and reliability</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-202">3\) Keď sa vyskytnú zlyhania, tieto signály vysielajú dôležité kódy zlyhania z príslušnej súčasti (kód klienta balíka Office, knižnice overovania alebo služby oprávnenia), ktoré je možné použiť na určenie priority, diagnostikovanie a zmierňovanie</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-202">3\) When failures occur, these signals emit important failure codes from the responsible component (Office client code, authentication libraries, or authority services) which can be used for triage, diagnosis and mitigation</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-203">4\) Tieto signály slúžia ako vstupy pre rôzne monitory pripravenosti na odoslanie a monitory stavu, ktoré odosielajú upozornenia, vďaka ktorým naši inžinieri môžu rýchlo reagovať a skrátiť čas na zmiernenie kritických chýb blokujúcich používateľa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-203">4\) These signals power various ship readiness and health monitors which fire alerts so our engineers can engage quickly and reduce the time to mitigation of critical user-blocking failures</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-204">Zhromažďujú sa tieto polia:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-204">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-205">**AllowSavedCreds** – či sú nové poverenia trvalé</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-205">**AllowSavedCreds** - whether the new credential is persisted</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-206">**AuthScheme** – používaná schéma overovania</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-206">**AuthScheme** - the authentication scheme used</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-207">**CredsSaved** – či sú nové poverenia uložené</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-207">**CredsSaved** - whether the new credential is saved</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-208">**DocumentUrlHash** – vyžadovanie šifrovanej URL adresy</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-208">**DocumentUrlHash** - the encrypted URL requesting</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-209">**EndTag** – značka, v ktorej sa výzva skončila</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-209">**EndTag** - the tag where the prompt ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-210">**NewIdentity**\_ErrorState – či je nová identita platná</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-210">**NewIdentity**\_ErrorState – whether the new identity is valid</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-211">**NewIdentity\_HashedUniqueId** – šifrovaný identifikátor novej identity po skončení výzvy</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-211">**NewIdentity\_HashedUniqueId** - the encrypted new identity ID after prompt is completed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-212">**NewIdentity\_ProviderType** – poskytovateľ novej identity po skončení výzvy</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-212">**NewIdentity\_ProviderType** - the new identity provider after the prompt is completed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-213">**NewIdentity\_UniqueID** – identifikátor novej identity po skončení výzvy</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-213">**NewIdentity\_UniqueID** - the new identity ID after the prompt is completed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-214">**OutStatus** – či je výstup výzvy platný</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-214">**OutStatus** - whether the prompt output is valid</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-215">**PromptEndTime** – čas skončenia výzvy</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-215">**PromptEndTime** - the time when the prompt ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-216">**PromptFailedTag** – značka, ktorá signalizuje zlyhanie výzvy SSPI</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-216">**PromptFailedTag** - the tag that indicates SSPI prompt failure</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-217">**PromptFlow** – značka, ktorá vyvolala výzvu SSPI</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-217">**PromptFlow** - the tag that invoked the SSPI prompt</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-218">**PromptStartTime** – čas začatia výzvy</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-218">**PromptStartTime** - the time when the prompt started</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-219">**Proxy** – či sa používa server proxy</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-219">**Proxy** - if proxy is used</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-220">**ServerHash** – šifrovaná adresa servera</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-220">**ServerHash** - the encrypted server address</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-221">**SessionEndTime** – čas skončenia relácie udalosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-221">**SessionEndTime** - the time when the event session ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-222">**Timeout** – čas uplynutia časového limitu výzvy</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-222">**Timeout** - the time when the prompt is timed out</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-223">**UiMessage** – hlásenie používateľského rozhrania vo výzve</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-223">**UiMessage** - the UI message in the prompt</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-224">**UserNameHash** – šifrované meno používateľa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-224">**UserNameHash** - the encrypted user name</span></span>

### <a name="officeidentitywin32prompt"></a><span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-225">Office.Identity.Win32Prompt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-225">Office.Identity.Win32Prompt</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-226">Zhromažďuje sa, keď sa v balíku Office používateľovi zobrazí výzva na prihlásenie s viacfaktorovým overovaním.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-226">Collected when Office shows the user a multi-factor authentication sign-in prompt.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-227">Spolu so získaním skrytého tokenu výzvy na overenie umožňujú určiť, či sa používateľ nachádza v stave nefunkčného overenia, čo pre používateľa znamená, že je stave offline klienta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-227">Along with silent token acquisitions, authentication prompts determine whether a user is in a broken authentication state, which results in an Offline Client state.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-228">Nefunkčné overenie môže znemožniť získanie licencie a mať tak za následok, že klient bude úplne nepoužiteľný.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-228">Broken authentication may prevent license acquisition and result in a completely unusable client.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-229">Tieto udalosti, ako aj udalosti priestoru názvov Office.MATS, sa používajú na tieto účely:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-229">These events, along with the Office.MATS namespace events, are used for the following purposes:</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-231">2\) Vyhodnotenie, či zmeny, ku ktorým došlo v klientovi alebo v službách, mali za následok kritické regresie pri postupe alebo spoľahlivosti overovania používateľa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-231">2\) Evaluate whether changes that have occurred on the client or services have resulted in critical regressions in the user's authentication experience and reliability</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-232">3\) Keď sa vyskytnú zlyhania, tieto signály vysielajú dôležité kódy zlyhania z príslušnej súčasti (kód klienta balíka Office, knižnice overovania alebo služby oprávnenia), ktoré je možné použiť na určenie priority, diagnostikovanie a zmierňovanie</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-232">3\) When failures occur, these signals emit important failure codes from the responsible component (Office client code, authentication libraries, or authority services) which can be used for triage, diagnosis and mitigation</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-233">4\) Tieto signály slúžia ako vstupy pre rôzne monitory pripravenosti na odoslanie a monitory stavu, ktoré odosielajú upozornenia, vďaka ktorým naši inžinieri môžu rýchlo reagovať a skrátiť čas na zmiernenie kritických chýb blokujúcich používateľa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-233">4\) These signals power various ship readiness and health monitors which fire alerts so our engineers can engage quickly and reduce the time to mitigation of critical user-blocking failures.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-234">Zhromažďujú sa tieto polia:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-234">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-235">**AdalWAMUsed** – značka, ktorá označuje výsledok, ak sa používa ADAL-atop-WAM</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-235">**AdalWAMUsed** – the tag that indicates result if ADAL-atop-WAM is used</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-236">**CallTag** – značka, ktorá označuje volajúceho používateľského rozhrania prihlásenia</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-236">**CallTag** – the tag that indicates the caller of sign in UI</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-237">**Context** – kontext prihlásenia pre výzvu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-237">**Context** - the sign in context for the prompt</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-238">**EndTagIdentityProviderRequested** – značka, v ktorej sa vyžaduje poskytovateľ identity</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-238">**EndTagIdentityProviderRequested** - the tag where the identity provider is requested</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-242">**LastLoginDelta** – čas od posledného úspešného prihlásenia</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-242">**LastLoginDelta** - the time delta from last successful login</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-244">**NewIdentity\_ProviderType** – typ poskytovateľa novej identity po výzve</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-244">**NewIdentity\_ProviderType** - the new identity provider type after prompt</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-245">**NewIdentity\_UniqueID** – identifikátor novej identity po výzve</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-245">**NewIdentity\_UniqueID** - the new identity ID returned after prompt</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-246">**PromptCorrelation** – identifikátor korelácie výzvy na diagnostické účely</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-246">**PromptCorrelation** - the prompt correlation ID for diagnostic purpose</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-248">**PromptStartTime** – čas začatia výzvy</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-248">**PromptStartTime** – the time when the prompt started</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-249">**SessionEndTime** – čas skončenia relácie udalosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-249">**SessionEndTime** - the time when the event session ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-250">**ShowUIResult** – kód výsledku vrátený z používateľského rozhrania výzvy</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-250">**ShowUIResult** – the result code returned from the prompt UI</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-251">**StartTag** – značka, v ktorej sa začala výzva Win32</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-251">**StartTag** – the tag where Win32 prompt started</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-253">**WasIdentitySignedOut** – či je používateľ odhlásený</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-253">**WasIdentitySignedOut** - whether the user is signed out</span></span>

### <a name="officematsactionofficewin32-officematsactionofficewinrt"></a><span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-254">Office.MATS.actionofficewin32, Office.MATS.actionofficewinrt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-254">Office.MATS.actionofficewin32, Office.MATS.actionofficewinrt</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-255">Nasledujúci popis sa vzťahuje na udalosti platformy Win32 aj WinRT (názov závisí od platformy.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-255">The following description applies for both Win32 and WinRT events (the name depends on platform.)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-256">Microsoft Auth Telemetry System (MATS) sa zhromažďuje, keď sa Office pokúša získať token overenia, či už bez zobrazenia výzvy alebo prostredníctvom zobrazenia výzvy.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-256">Microsoft Auth Telemetry System (MATS) is collected when Office attempts to acquire an authentication token, either silently or through prompting.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-257">Keď pokusy o získanie zlyhajú, zahrnú sa aj informácie o chybe.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-257">When acquisition attempts fail, error information is included.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-258">Tieto udalosti pomáhajú našim používateľom vyhnúť sa prechodu do stavu nefunkčného overenia:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-258">These events help our users avoid entering broken authentication states by:</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-259">1\) Identifikáciou, či klienti dokážu úspešne získať overovací token alebo či prešli do stavu nefunkčného overenia.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-259">1\) Identifying whether clients can successfully obtain an authentication token or have entered a broken authentication state.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-260">2\) Vyhodnotením, či zmeny, ku ktorým došlo v klientovi alebo v službách, mali za následok kritické regresie pri postupe alebo spoľahlivosti overovania používateľa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-260">2\) Evaluate when changes occur on the client or services, whether they result in critical regressions in the user's authentication experience and reliability</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-261">3\) Keď sa vyskytnú zlyhania, tieto signály vysielajú dôležité kódy zlyhania z príslušnej súčasti (kód klienta balíka Office, knižnice overovania alebo služby oprávnenia), ktoré je možné použiť na určenie priority, diagnostikovanie a zmierňovanie</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-261">3\) When failures occur, these signals emit important failure codes from the responsible component (Office client code, authentication libraries, or authority services) which can be used for triage, diagnosis and mitigation</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-262">4\) Tieto signály slúžia ako vstupy pre rôzne monitory pripravenosti na odoslanie a monitory stavu, ktoré odosielajú upozornenia, vďaka ktorým naši inžinieri môžu rýchlo reagovať a skrátiť čas na zmiernenie kritických chýb</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-262">4\) These signals power various ship readiness and health monitors which fire alerts so our engineers can engage quickly and reduce the time to mitigation of critical failures.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-263">Zhromažďujú sa tieto polia:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-263">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-264">**Actiontype** – ktorá knižnica overovania sa používa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-264">**Actiontype** - Which authentication library is used</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-265">**Appaudience** – či je zostava aplikácie na interné alebo externé používanie</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-265">**Appaudience** - Is the app build for internal or external use</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-266">**Appforcedprompt** – či aplikácia prepísala vyrovnávaciu pamäť a vynútila zobrazenie výzvy</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-266">**Appforcedprompt** - Did the app override cache and force a prompt to be shown</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-267">**Appname** – názov aplikácie, ktorá vykonáva overovanie</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-267">**Appname** - Name of the application doing authentication</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-268">**Appver** – verzia aplikácie, ktorá vykonáva overovanie</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-268">**Appver** - Version of the application doing authentication</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-269">**Askedforcreds** – či sa v aplikácii zobrazila výzva pre používateľa na zadanie poverení pre túto akciu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-269">**Askedforcreds** - Did the application ask the user to enter credentials for this action</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-270">**Authoutcome** – či bol pokus o overenie úspešný, zlyhal alebo bol zrušený</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-270">**Authoutcome** - Did the authentication attempt succeed, fail, or was canceled</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-271">**Blockingprompt** – či sa v aplikácii zobrazila výzva vyžadujúca interakciu používateľa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-271">**Blockingprompt** - Did the application throw a prompt requiring user interaction</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-272">**Correlationid** – identifikátor GUID, ktorý sa použil na spojenie s údajmi služby</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-272">**Correlationid** - GUID used for joining with services data</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-273">**Count** – počet udalostí v prípadoch agregácie</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-273">**Count** - Count of events in cases of aggregation</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-274">**Data\_accounttype** – spotrebiteľské konto alebo konto organizácie</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-274">**Data\_accounttype** - Consumer or organizational account</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-275">**Devicenetworkstate** – či bol používateľ online</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-275">**Devicenetworkstate** - Was the user online</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-276">**Deviceprofiletelemetryid** – anonymný identifikátor zariadenia, ktorý sa používa na meranie výkonu zariadenia</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-276">**Deviceprofiletelemetryid** - Anonymous device ID used to measure device experience</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-277">**Duration** – dĺžka trvania overovania</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-277">**Duration** - How long the authentication took</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-278">**Endtime** – čas skončenia udalosti overovania</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-278">**Endtime** - When the authentication event ended</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-279">**Error** – kód chyby, ak overovanie zlyhalo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-279">**Error** - Error code if the authentication failed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-280">**Errordescription** – stručný popis chyby</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-280">**Errordescription** - Brief description of the error</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-281">**Errorsource** – či chyba pochádzala zo služby, knižnice overovania alebo aplikácie</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-281">**Errorsource** - Did the error come from service, authentication library, or application</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-282">**Identityservice** – či bola vyvolaná služba Microsoft Service Account (MSA) alebo Azure Active Directory (AAD)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-282">**Identityservice** - Was Microsoft Service Account (MSA) or Azure Active Directory (AAD) service invoked</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-283">**Interactiveauthcontainer** – aký typ výzvy sa zobrazil</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-283">**Interactiveauthcontainer** - What type of prompt was shown</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-284">**Issilent** – či sa výzva zobrazila</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-284">**Issilent** - Was a prompt shown</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-285">**Microsoft**\_**ADAL**\_**adal**\_**version** – verzia knižnice Azure Active Directory Authentication Library (ADAL)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-285">**Microsoft**\_**ADAL**\_**adal**\_**version** - Version of the Azure Active Directory Authentication Library (ADAL)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-286">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_api\_error\_code** – kód chyby vyslaný knižnicou overovania pre tento pokus o overenie</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-286">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_api\_error\_code** - Error code emitted by authentication library for this authentication attempt</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-287">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_api\_id** – rozhranie API vyvolané pre tento pokus o overenie</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-287">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_api\_id** - API invoked for this authentication attempt</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-288">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_authority** – URL adresa autority služby Azure Active Directory zodpovednej za overovanie používateľa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-288">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_authority** – Azure Active Directory authority URL responsible for authenticating the user</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-289">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_authority\_type** – spotrebiteľské/Microsoft Service Agreement (MSA) alebo organizačné/Azure Active Directory (AAD); v súčasnosti vždy AAD</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-289">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_authority\_type** – Consumer / Microsoft Service Agreement (MSA) vs organizational / Azure Active Directory (AAD); currently always AAD</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-290">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_authority\_validation\_status** – signalizuje, či sa overovanie dokončilo na strane služby</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-290">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_authority\_validation\_status** – Tells whether authentication completed on the service-side</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-291">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_broker\_app** – signalizuje, či knižnica ADAL použila sprostredkovateľa na overenie</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-291">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_broker\_app** - Tells whether ADAL used a broker for authentication</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-292">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_broker\_app\_used** – uvádza názov sprostredkovateľa (napr. Windows Account Management)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-292">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_broker\_app\_used** – Tells the name of the broker (e.g., Windows Account Management)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-293">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_broker\_version** – uvádza verziu sprostredkovateľa, ak sa použil</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-293">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_broker\_version** - Tells the version of the broker if used</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-294">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_event\_count** – počet udalostí vyrovnávacej pamäte, ktoré knižnica ADAL vykonala počas načítavania tokenu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-294">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_event\_count** - Number of cache events ADAL performed while retrieving token</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-295">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_event\_count\_max** – ak je tento signál agregovaný, max. počet udalostí vyrovnávacej pamäte ktorejkoľvek z agregovaných udalostí.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-295">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_event\_count\_max** - If this signal is aggregated, max cache events of any one of the aggregated events.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-296">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_event\_count\_min** – ak je tento signál agregovaný, min. počet udalostí vyrovnávacej pamäte ktorejkoľvek z agregovaných udalostí.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-296">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_event\_count\_min** - If this signal is aggregated, min cache events of any one of the aggregated events.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-297">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_event\_count\_sum** – ak je tento signál agregovaný, súčet udalostí vyrovnávacej pamäte všetkých agregovaných udalostí.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-297">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_event\_count\_sum** - If this signal is aggregated, sum of the cache events of all the aggregated events.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-298">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_read\_count** – koľkokrát rozhranie API čítalo z vyrovnávacej pamäte disku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-298">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_read\_count** - How many times the API read from the disk cache.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-299">Je prítomné, ak došlo k aspoň jednému čítaniu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-299">Present if there was at least one read.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-300">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_read\_error\_count** – koľkokrát zlyhalo čítanie z vyrovnávacej pamäte disku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-300">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_read\_error\_count** - How many times the disk cache read failed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-301">Je prítomné, ak došlo k aspoň jednému zlyhaniu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-301">Is present if there was at least one failure.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-302">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_read\_last\_error** – kód chyby knižnice ADAL.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-302">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_read\_last\_error** - ADAL error code.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-303">Je prítomné, ak došlo k aspoň jednému zlyhaniu čítania.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-303">Present if there was at least one read failure.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-304">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_read\_last\_system\_error** – kód systémovej chyby.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-304">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_read\_last\_system\_error** - System error code.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-305">Je prítomné, ak došlo k aspoň jednému zlyhaniu čítania.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-305">Is present if there was at least one read failure.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-306">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_write\_count** – koľkokrát rozhranie API zapísalo do vyrovnávacej pamäte disku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-306">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_write\_count** - How many times the API wrote to the disk cache.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-307">Je prítomné, ak došlo k aspoň jednému zapisovaniu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-307">Present if there was at least one write.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-308">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_write\_error\_count** – koľkokrát zlyhalo zapisovanie do vyrovnávacej pamäte disku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-308">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_write\_error\_count** - How many times the disk cache-write failed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-309">Je prítomné, ak došlo k aspoň jednému zlyhaniu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-309">Present if there was at least one failure.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-310">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_write\_last\_error** – kód chyby knižnice ADAL.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-310">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_write\_last\_error** - ADAL error code.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-311">Je prítomné, ak došlo k aspoň jednému zlyhaniu zapisovania.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-311">Present if there was at least one write failure.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-312">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_write\_last\_system\_error** – kód systémovej chyby.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-312">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_cache\_write\_last\_system\_error** - System error code.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-313">Je prítomné, ak došlo k aspoň jednému zlyhaniu zapisovania.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-313">Present if there was at least one write failure.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-314">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_client\_id** – hashovaný identifikátor aplikácie služby AAD</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-314">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_client\_id** - Hashed AAD app ID</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-315">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_extended\_expires\_on\_setting** – pravda/nepravda, uvádza, či token má predĺženú životnosť.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-315">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_extended\_expires\_on\_setting** - True/false telling if the token has an extended lifetime.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-316">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_http\_event\_count** – počet HTTP volaní uskutočnených knižnicou ADAL.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-316">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_http\_event\_coun**t - Count of HTTP calls made by ADAL.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-317">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_http\_event\_count\_max** – ak je tento signál agregovaný, max. počet HTTP volaní uskutočnených knižnicou ADAL ktorejkoľvek agregovanej udalosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-317">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_http\_event\_count\_max** - If this signal is aggregated, max HTTP calls made by ADAL of any aggregated event.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-318">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_http\_event\_count\_min** – ak je tento signál agregovaný, min. počet HTTP volaní uskutočnených knižnicou ADAL ktorejkoľvek agregovanej udalosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-318">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_http\_event\_count\_min** - If this signal is aggregated, min HTTP calls made by ADAL of any aggregated event.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-319">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_http\_event\_count\_sum** – ak je tento signál agregovaný, súčet HTTP volaní uskutočnených knižnicou ADAL všetkých agregovaných udalostí.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-319">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_http\_event\_count\_sum** - If this signal is aggregated, sum of the HTTP calls made by ADAL of all the aggregated events.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-320">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_is\_silent\_ui** – pravda/nepravda, uvádza, či knižnica ADAL zobrazila používateľské rozhranie (výzvu).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-320">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_is\_silent\_ui** - True/false telling if UI was shown (prompt) by ADAL.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-322">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_logging\_pii\_enabled** – pravda/nepravda, uvádza, či je povolený režim úplného zapisovania do denníka knižnice ADAL.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-322">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_logging\_pii\_enabled** - True/false telling if ADAL full logging mode is enabled.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-323">Tieto údaje sa zapisujú do denníka len lokálne, neodosielajú sa v telemetrii.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-323">This data is only logged locally, not emitted in telemetry.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-324">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_oauth\_error\_code** – kód chyby protokolu OAuth vrátený službou.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-324">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_oauth\_error\_code** – OAuth protocol error code returned by the service.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-325">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_prompt\_behavior** – prihlasovací alebo žiaden HTTP parameter odovzdaný do služby na určenie, či je možné zobraziť používateľské rozhranie.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-325">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_prompt\_behavior** - log-in or none HTTP parameter passed to service to specify if user interface can be shown.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-326">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_request\_id** – transakčný identifikátor GUID pre požiadavky vyslaný knižnicou do služby.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-326">**Microsoft\_ADAL\_request\_id** - Transactional GUID for the request emitted by ADAL to the service.</span></span>

### <a name="officeclicktorunbootstrapper"></a><span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-377">Office.ClickToRun.Bootstrapper</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-377">Office.ClickToRun.Bootstrapper</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-378">Údaje o inštalácii a inventári balíka Office zhromažďované, keď používateľ spustí súbor setup.exe balíka Office na úpravu nainštalovaných produktov balíka Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-378">Office set up and inventory data collected when the user is running Office setup.exe to modify their installed Office products.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-379">Používa sa na meranie úspechu alebo neúspechu úplnej inštalácie balíka Office spustenej používateľom vrátane predbežných nevyhnutných kontrol.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-379">Used to measure success / failure of a full user-initiated Office installation including pre-requisite checks.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-380">Zhromažďujú sa tieto polia:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-380">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-381">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_ErrorCode** – kód chyby zlyhania</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-381">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_ErrorCode** – The error code we failed with</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-382">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_ErrorSource** – funkcia, v ktorej došlo k zlyhaniu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-382">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_ErrorSource** – The function we failed in</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-383">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_FailingState** – časť, v ktorej došlo k zlyhaniu v bootstrapper</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-383">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_FailingState** – The part that we failed in the boostrapperbootstrapper</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-384">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_OExceptionType** – typ výnimky zlyhania</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-384">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_OExceptionType** – The type of exception we failed with</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-385">**Data\_Culture** – jazyková verzia, s ktorou sa spúšťa súbor exe, t. j. en-us</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-385">**Data\_Culture** - the culture we are running this exe with, i.e. en-us</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-386">**Data\_HashedOLSToken** – sha-256 hash tokenu, ktoré nám služba OLS poskytuje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-386">**Data\_HashedOLSToken** - a sha-256 hash of a token the OLS service gives us</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-387">**Data\_Platform** – inštalácia typu x64 alebo x86</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-387">**Data\_Platform** - x64 or x86 install</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-388">**Data\_PrereqFailure\_Type** – zlyhanie základnej požiadavky, ktoré sa vyskytlo, napr. operačný súbor nie je podporovaný</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-388">**Data\_PrereqFailure\_Type** – The prerequisite failure we hit, i.e. the operating system is not supported</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-389">**Data\_ProductReleaseId** – produkt, ktorý inštalujeme, t. j. Aplikácie Microsoft 365 pre veľké organizácie</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-389">**Data\_ProductReleaseId** - Product we're installing, i.e. Microsoft 365 Apps for enterprise</span></span>

### <a name="officeclicktoruncorruptioncheck"></a><span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-390">Office.ClickToRun.CorruptionCheck</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-390">Office.ClickToRun.CorruptionCheck</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-391">Údaje o inštalácii a inventári balíka Office zhromažďované, keď klient služby Klikni a spusti spustil kontrolu poškodenia na zaistenie správnosti binárnych súborov balíka Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-391">Office set up and inventory data collected when Click-to-Run client is running a corruption check to make sure that Office binaries are correct.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-392">Používa sa na meranie poškodenia binárnych súborov balíka Office a na určenie, ktoré binárne súbory sú poškodené.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-392">Used to measure corruption of Office binaries, and which binaries are corrupt.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-393">Zhromažďujú sa tieto polia:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-393">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-394">**Data\_Active** – aktuálny manifest streamu, ktorý sa kontroluje na disku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-394">**Data\_Active -** The current stream manifest we're checking on disk</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-395">**Data\_ActivePackages** – ktoré balíky manifest obsahuje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-395">**Data\_ActivePackages -** what packages the manifest contains</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-396">**Data\_ActiveVersion** – verzia manifestu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-396">**Data\_ActiveVersion -** the version of the manifest</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-397">**Data\_AddFileCount** – koľko súborov sa pridáva</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-397">**Data\_AddFileCount -** how many files we're adding</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-398">**Data\_AddFileFiles** – vzorka súborov, ktoré sa pridávajú</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-398">**Data\_AddFileFiles -** a sample of the files we're adding</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-399">**Data\_CompressionLevel** – ako sú súbory komprimované</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-399">**Data\_CompressionLevel -** how the files are compressed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-400">**Data\_CorruptionCheckLevel** – ako podrobne sa kontroluje poškodenie, fázy</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-400">**Data\_CorruptionCheckLevel -** how deeply we're checking for corruption, stages</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-401">**Data\_CorruptSizeCount** – koľko súborov má poškodenú veľkosť</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-401">**Data\_CorruptSizeCount -** how many files have a corrupt size</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-402">**Data\_CorruptSizeFiles** – vzorka súborov, ktoré majú poškodenú veľkosť</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-402">**Data\_CorruptSizeFiles -** a sample of the files that have a corrupted size</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-403">**Data\_CorruptVersonCount** – koľko súborov má poškodenú veľkosť</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-403">**Data\_CorruptVersionCount -** how many files have a corrupted version</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-404">**Data\_CorruptVersionFiles** – vzorka súborov, ktoré majú poškodenú verziu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-404">**Data\_CorruptVersionFiles -** a sample of the files that have a corrupted version</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-405">**Data\_FileBadDigestCount** – koľko súborov sa nepodarilo otvoriť</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-405">**Data\_FileBadDigestCount -** how many files we failed to open</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-407">**Data\_FileNotSignedCount** – koľko súborov nie je podpísaných</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-407">**Data\_FileNotSignedCount -** have many files that aren't signed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-446">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_ErrorSource** – funkcia, v ktorej došlo k zlyhaniu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-446">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_ErrorSource-** The function we failed in</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-447">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_FailingState** – časť, v ktorej došlo k zlyhaniu v bootstrapper</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-447">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_FailingState-** The part that we failed in the boot-strapper</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-448">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_OExceptionType** – typ výnimky zlyhania</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-448">**Data\_BootStrapperStateFailure\_OExceptionType-** The type of exception we failed with</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-449">**Data\_ConfigurationHost** – hostiteľ, od ktorého pochádza súbor configuration.xml</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-449">**Data\_ConfigurationHost-** The host where the configuration.xml came from</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-450">**Data\_ConfigurationId** – identifikátor získaný zo súboru configuration.xml</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-450">**Data\_ConfigurationId-** The ID we get from a configuration.xml</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-451">**Data\_ConfigurationSource** – zdroj súboru configuration.xml</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-451">**Data\_ConfigurationSource-** We the configuration.xml came from</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-452">**Data\_Culture** – jazyková verzia, s ktorou sa spúšťa súbor exe, t. j. en-us</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-452">**Data\_Culture-** the culture we are running this exe with, i.e. en-us</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-453">**Data\_HashedOLSToken** – sha-256 hash tokenu, ktoré nám služba OLS poskytuje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-453">**Data\_HashedOLSToken-** a sha-256 hash of a token the OLS service gives us</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-454">**Data\_MigrateArchRequest** – či sa používateľ migruje z x86 na x64 alebo naopak</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-454">**Data\_MigrateArchRequest-** If we are migrating the user from x86 to x64 or vice-versa</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-455">**Data\_MigrateArchRequestValid** – či je požiadavka na migráciu platná</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-455">**Data\_MigrateArchRequestValid-** If we believe the migrate request is valid</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-456">**Data\_Platform** – inštalácia typu x64 alebo x86</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-456">**Data\_Platform-** x64 or x86 install</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-457">**Data\_PlatformMigratedFrom** – počiatočná platforma, t. j. x86</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-457">**Data\_PlatformMigratedFrom-** Starting platform, i.e. x86</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-458">**Data\_PlatformMigratedTo** – výsledná platforma, t j. x64</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-458">**Data\_PlatformMigratedTo-** Ending platform, i.e. x64</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-459">**Data\_PrereqFailure\_Type** – predbežné zlyhanie, ktoré sa vyskytlo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-459">**Data\_PrereqFailure\_Type-** The prerequisite failure we hit</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-460">**Data\_ProductReleaseId** – produkt, ktorý inštalujeme, t. j. Aplikácie Microsoft 365 pre veľké organizácie</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-460">**Data\_ProductReleaseId-** Product we're installing, i.e. Microsoft 365 Apps for enterprise</span></span>

### <a name="officeclicktorunrepomanlogger"></a><span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-461">Office.ClickToRun.RepomanLogger</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-461">Office.ClickToRun.RepomanLogger</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-462">Hlási stav nového kanála aktualizácií Klikni a spusti („Repoman“) a či boli aktualizácie balíka Office úspešne stiahnuté a použité.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-462">Reports on the status for the new Click-to-Run update pipeline ("Repoman") and if it successfully downloads and applies Office updates.</span></span>

V opačnom prípade má hodnotu false.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-464">**ApplySucceeded -** True if the pipeline successfully applied an Office update, false if not.</span></span>
  
  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-465">**DownloadSucceeded** – hodnota true označuje, že kanál úspešne stiahol aktualizáciu balíka Office. V opačnom prípade má hodnotu false.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-465">**DownloadSucceeded -** True if the pipeline successfully downloaded an Office update, false if not.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-466">**ErrorCode** – kód poslednej chyby, ku ktorej došlo v kanáli Klikni a spusti (Repoman).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-466">**ErrorCode -** The code of the last error that occurred in the Click-to-Run Repoman pipeline.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-467">**ErrorDetails** – ďalšie informácie o chybe, ku ktorej došlo v kanáli Klikni a spusti (Repoman).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-467">**ErrorDetails -**  Additional error details of the last error that occurred in the Click-to-Run Repoman pipeline.</span></span>
 
  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-468">**ErrorMessage** – hlásenie poslednej chyby, ku ktorej došlo v kanáli Klikni a spusti (Repoman).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-468">**ErrorMessage -** The message of the last error that occurred in the Click-to-Run Repoman pipeline.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-469">**OpenStreamSessionSucceeded** – hodnota true označuje, že kanál úspešne vytvoril reláciu na streamovanie aktualizácie balíka Office. V opačnom prípade má hodnotu false.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-469">**OpenStreamSessionSucceeded -** True if the pipeline successfully creates a session for streaming an Office update, false if not.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-470">**RepomanErrorMessage** – chybové hlásenie prijaté z knižnice repoman.dll.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-470">**RepomanErrorMessage -** The error message received from the repoman.dll.</span></span>

### <a name="officeclicktoruntransport"></a><span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1405">Office.ClickToRun.Transport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1405">Office.ClickToRun.Transport</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1406">Táto udalosť nahlasuje akcie sťahovania súborov s cieľom určiť úspešnosť operácie, typ vykonaného sťahovania a diagnostické informácie.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1406">Reports on the file download actions to determine the success of the operation, type of download performed and diagnostic information.</span></span>


- <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1407">**BytesFromGroupPeers** – počet bajtov z partnerských zariadení v skupine, iba na sťahovanie pomocou optimalizácie doručovania</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1407">**BytesFromGroupPeers -**    Bytes from group peers, only for downloads using Delivery Optimization</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1408">**BytesFromHttp** – počet bajtov z protokolu http, iba na sťahovanie pomocou optimalizácie doručovania</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1408">**BytesFromHttp -**     Bytes from http, only for downloads using Delivery Optimization</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1409">**BytesFromInternetPeers** – počet bajtov z partnerských zariadení na internete, iba na sťahovanie pomocou optimalizácie doručovania</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1409">**ByteFromInternetPeers -**    Bytes from internet peers, only for downloads using Delivery Optimization</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1410">**BytesFromLanPeers** – počet bajtov z partnerských zariadení v sieti LAN, iba na sťahovanie pomocou optimalizácie doručovania</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1410">**BytesFromLanPeers -**    Bytes from Lan peers, only for downloads using Delivery Optimization</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1411">**CancelledJobs** – počet zrušených žiadostí v relácii</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1411">**canceledJobs -**     Number of canceled requests in the session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1412">**Connected** – či je pripojené k zdroju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1412">**Connected -**    Whether connected to source</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1413">**ErrorCode** – kód poslednej chyby</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1413">**ErrorCode -**    The code of last error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1414">**ErrorDetails** – podrobnosti poslednej chyby</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1414">**ErrorDetails -**     The detail of last error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1416">**ErrorSource** – zdroj poslednej chyby (napr. pripojenie, načítanie súboru alebo načítanie rozsahu)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1416">**ErrorSource -**    The source of last error, e.g. Connection, LoadFile or LoadRange</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1417">**FailedJobs** – počet zlyhaných žiadostí v relácii</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1417">**FailedJob -**    Number of failed requests in the session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1418">**FileSize** – veľkosť zdroja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1418">**FileSize -**    Size of the resource</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1419">**SourcePathNoFilePath** – zdrojová cesta k zdroju, len zdroj http sa hlási, cesta k lokálnemu súboru alebo cesta UNC sa filtruje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1419">**SourcePathNoFilePath -**    Source path of the resource only http source is reported, local file path or UNC path is filtered</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1421">**TotalJobs** – celkový počet žiadostí v relácii</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1421">**TotalJobs -**     Total number of requests in the session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1422">**TotalRequestedBytes** – celkový počet bajtov v relácii</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1422">**TotalRequestedBytes -**     Total requested bytes in the session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1516">**Origin** – reťazcová hodnota, ktorá uvádza, ktorý z podporovaných pôvodov (Portoriko [PR], Singapur [SG], Dublin [DB]) sa má použiť na úvodné streamovanie inštalácie</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1516">**Origin –**    String value telling us which of the supported origins (Puerto Rico [PR], Singapore [SG], Dublin [DB]) should be used for initial installation streaming</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1536">**DeliveryMechanism** – Identifikátor GUID „FFNRoot“ extrahovaný z formátu XML deskriptora verzie (s pečiatkou RDX), ktorý uvádza, z ktorého publika/kanála zdroj zostavy pochádzal</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1536">**DeliveryMechanism –**    The "FFNRoot" guid extracted from the Version Descriptor XML (stamped by RDX), which tells us which audience/channel the build source came from</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1539">**ErrorDetails** – reťazec, ktorý popisuje umiestnenie, v ktorom sa vyskytla nespracovaná výnimka (funkcia, súbor, číslo riadka, ďalšie parametre určené pri výskyte výnimky)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1539">**ErrorDetails –**    String that describes the location of where an unhandled exception occurred (function, file, line number, additional parameters set by the thrower)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1541">**ErrorType** – reťazec popisujúci kategóriu nespracovanej výnimky</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1541">**ErrorType –**    String describing the category of an unhandled exception</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1542">**ExitCode** – celočíselná hodnota súvisiaca s výsledkom spustenia fázy Execute súčasti Bootstrapper, ktorá signalizuje úspech alebo špecifické typy zlyhania</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1542">**ExitCode –**    Integer value associated with the result of running the Execute phase of the bootstrapper, indicating success vs. specific types of failure</span></span>

### <a name="officeserviceabilitymanagerinventoryaddonheartbeat"></a><span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1548">Office.ServiceabilityManager.InventoryAddon.Heartbeat</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1548">Office.ServiceabilityManager.InventoryAddon.Heartbeat</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1549">*[Táto udalosť sa odstránila z aktuálnych zostáv balíka Office, ale stále sa môže zobraziť v starších zostavách.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1549">*[This event has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1550">Táto udalosť sa používa na získanie štandardných metaúdajov pri každom spustení doplnku Inventory, ktorý je súčasťou programu Office Serviceability Manager a používa sa na informácie o inventári balíka Office o zariadeniach, pre ktoré sa správca IT rozhodol.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1550">This event is used to acquire standard metadata on each run of the Inventory add-on, which is part of the Office Serviceability Manager and is used for inventory Office information on those machines for which an IT admin has opted in.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1551">Metaúdaj, ktoré nás obzvlášť zaujíma, sú ID relácie, a používa sa na prepojenie na iné údaje uložené v rámci cloudovej služby na nájomníka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1551">The metadata of specific interest here is the session ID, and it is used for linking to other data stored within a per-tenant cloud service.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1552">Táto udalosť neobsahuje žiadne dodatočné polia, pretože len metaúdaje sú relevantné.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1552">This event contains no extra fields since only the metadata is relevant.</span></span>

### <a name="officeserviceabilitymanagerinventoryaddonresults"></a><span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1553">Office.ServiceabilityManager.InventoryAddon.Results</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1553">Office.ServiceabilityManager.InventoryAddon.Results</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1554">Táto udalosť sa zaznamená, keď sa dokončí volanie webovej služby uskutočnené v rámci doplnku Click-to-Run Serviceability Manager Inventory, a to bez ohľadu na to, či je úspešné alebo zlyhá.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1554">This event is logged when the call to the webservice made within the Click-to-Run Serviceability Manager Inventory add-on completes, irrespective of whether it succeeds or fails.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1555">Je to v podstate posledná operácia v rámci doplnku na sledovanie celkového stavu operácie.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1555">This is essentially the last operation within the add-on to track the overall operation status.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1556">Zhromažďujú sa tieto polia:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1556">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1557">**ActionDetail** – ďalšie podrobnosti pre prípad, že nastane porucha.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1557">**ActionDetail** -  Additional details for when a failure occurs.</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1558">Ak požiadavka HTTP uspeje, ActionDetail bude mať hodnotu 0.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1558">If the HTTP request succeeds, ActionDetail will be 0.</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1559">Ak pole Výsledok nie je v poriadku (t. j. hodnota nie je 0), čo znamená, že žiadosť sa neodoslala, v tomto poli sa zapíše interný kód chyby, ktorý je rovnaký ako pole Výsledok.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1559">If the Result field is not OK (i.e. not 0), which means that the request is not sent, this field will log the internal error code which is the same as the Result field.</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1560">Ak je pole Výsledok v poriadku (t. j. hodnota je 0), čo znamená, že kód odozvy HTTP > = 300, zapíše kód odozvy HTTP (napr. 404).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1560">If the Result field is OK (i.e. 0), which means that the HTTP response code >= 300, it will log the HTTP response code (e.g. 404).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1561">**Result** – príznaky číselného kódu chyby vrátené rozhraniami API volania webovej služby balíka Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1561">**Result** - Numeric error code flags returned by the Office webservice call APIs.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1562">– napr. 3 by znamenalo, že sa vyskytol problém s inicializáciou hlavičiek HTTP.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1562">– e.g. 3 would mean that there was a problem initializing the HTTP headers.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1563">**Type** – ďalšie informácie o type.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1563">**Type** - Additional type information.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1564">V prípade inventára sú tieto informácie špecifikované typom odosielanej údajovej časti – napr. úplná alebo len zmeny.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1564">In the case of the Inventory, this information specifies the type of payload being sent – e.g. full or just a delta of changes.</span></span> 

-  <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1565">**WebCallSource** – hodnota enumerácie (určená ako celé číslo), ktorá označuje doplnok Serviceability Manager  ktorý bol zdrojom volania:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1565">**WebCallSource** - An enumeration value (specified as an integer) indicating the Serviceability Manager add-on that was the source of the call:</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1566">Inventory: 0</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1566">Inventory: 0</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1567">Inventory Configuration: 1</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1567">Inventory Configuration: 1</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1568">Inventory Policy: 2</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1568">Inventory Policy: 2</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1569">Inventory Network Status: 3</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1569">Inventory Network Status: 3</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1570">Serviceability Manager: 4</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1570">Serviceability Manager: 4</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1571">Manageability: 5</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1571">Manageability: 5</span></span>

### <a name="officeserviceabilitymanagerwebservicefailure"></a><span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1572">Office.ServiceabilityManager.WebserviceFailure</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1572">Office.ServiceabilityManager.WebserviceFailure</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1573">Pri každom zlyhaní volania na WebService v rámci niektorého z doplnkov Office Serviceability Manager sa tento príkaz zapíše do denníka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1573">Whenever a call to a webservice within one of the Office Serviceability Manager add-ins fails, this statement is logged.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1574">Zlyhania môžu byť zapríčinené internými zlyhaniami alebo neschopnosťou pripojiť sa k WebService.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1574">Failures can be due to internal failures or an inability to connect to the webservice.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1575">Zhromažďujú sa tieto polia:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1575">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1576">**Add-on** – doplnok Click-to-Run Serviceability Manager, z ktorého sa uskutočnilo volanie webovej služby.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1576">**Add-on** - The Click-to-Run Serviceability Manager add-on from which the webservice call was made.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1577">Môže mať hodnoty ako inventory, manageability atď. zakódované ako číselná hodnota.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1577">This can have values like inventory, manageability, etc. encoded as a numeric value.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1578">**Correlation ID** – náhodne generovaný identifikátor GUID špecifický pre aktuálnu inštanciu, ktorý sa odosiela do webovej služby na koreláciu volaní medzi klientom a serverom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1578">**Correlation ID** - A randomly generated GUID specific to the current instance that is sent to the webservice to correlate calls between the client and the server.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1579">**ErrorInfo** – informácie o číselnom kóde chyby vrátené rozhraniami API volania webovej služby balíka Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1579">**ErrorInfo** - Numeric error code information returned by the Office webservice call APIs.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1580">**ErrorMessage** – správa, ktorá poskytuje ďalšie informácie o zlyhaní.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1580">**ErrorMessage** - A message providing further insight into the failure.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1581">Každý typ chyby sa priradí do pevne kódovaného reťazca, pričom určité typy chyby sa potenciálne priradia do viacerých reťazcov v závislosti od konkrétnej podstaty zlyhania.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1581">Each error type maps to a hardcoded string, with some error types mapping to potentially multiple strings depending on the specific nature of the failure.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1582">**Function** – funkcia v kóde, z ktorej sa uskutočnilo aktuálne volanie.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1582">**Function** - The function in the code from which the current call occurred.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1583">**Status** – kód stavu protokolu HTTP vrátený volaním do webovej služby, napríklad 404, 500 atď.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1583">**Status** - The HTTP status code returned by the call to the webservice, e.g. 404, 500, etc.</span></span>

### <a name="officeexperimentationtriggeranalysis"></a><span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1599">Office.Experimentation.TriggerAnalysis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1599">Office.Experimentation.TriggerAnalysis</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1600">Táto udalosť umožňuje obmedziť analýzu používania produktov a metrík výkonu (napríklad zlyhaní, zablokovaní a podobne) na podmnožinu používateľov alebo zariadení oprávnených na používanie danej funkcie, čím prispieva k zabezpečeniu správneho fungovania produktu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1600">This event helps scope analysis of product usage and performance metrics (such as crashes, hangs, etc.) to the subset of users or devices that are eligible to use the feature, thereby helping ensure that the product is working properly.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="f7dfc-1601">Zhromažďujú sa tieto polia:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f7dfc-1601">The following fields are collected:</span></span>
